{"Id":477,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-anonymousgroupo","Author":"Anonymous Group Of Translators","Language":"Chinese(traditional)","Description":"Chinese(traditional)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"Goodword Books , http://www.goodwordbooks.com/ , Center for Peace and Spirituality , https://www.cpsglobal.org/","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":16,"Text":"不然，你们却选择今世的 生活；"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":17,"Text":"其实，后世是更好的，是更久长的。"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":18,"Text":"这确是 载在古经典中的，"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":19,"Text":"载在易卜拉欣和穆萨的经典中的。"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"大灾的消息，确已降临你了，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"在那日，将有许多 449 人，是恭敬的、"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"劳动的、辛苦的，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"他们将入烈火，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"将饮沸泉，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"他们没有食物，但有荆棘，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"既不能肥 人，又不能充饥；"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"在那日，将有许多人，是享福的，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"是为其劳绩而愉快的，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"他们将在崇高的乐园中，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"听不到恶言，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":12,"Text":"里面有流泉，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":13,"Text":"里面有高榻，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":14,"Text":"有 陈设着的杯盏，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":15,"Text":"有排列着的靠枕，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":16,"Text":"有铺展开的绒 毯。"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":17,"Text":"难道他们不观察吗？骆驼是怎样造成的，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":18,"Text":"天是 怎样升高的，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":19,"Text":"山峦是怎样竖起的，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":20,"Text":"大地是怎样展开 的。"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":21,"Text":"你当教诲，你只是教诲（他们的），"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":22,"Text":"你绝不是 监察他们的，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":23,"Text":"但谁转身离去而且不信道，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":24,"Text":"真主将以 最大的刑罚惩治谁。"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":25,"Text":"他们必定只归于我，"},{"SurahNumber":88,"VerseNumber":26,"Text":"他们的稽 核，必定由我负责。"}]}